---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Fremont Sailing Club
description: The Fremont Sailing Club, established in 1968, is a family-oriented small boat sailing club in the San Francisco Bay Area.
---
<main>
  <section class="hero wrap" aria-label="Club header image">
    <img
      class="hero__image"
      src="assets/images/home/shoreline-lake-header.jpg"
      alt="Sailboats and docks at Shoreline Lake"
    />
  </section>

  <section class="intro wrap">
    <p class="intro__eyebrow">Est. in 1968</p>
    <h1>Fremont Sailing Club</h1>
    <p class="intro__tagline">
      “The finest small boat sailing club in the San Francisco Bay area”
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="events wrap" aria-labelledby="events-heading">
    <div class="events__media card card--photo">
      <img
        src="assets/images/home/action-photo.jpg"
        alt="A sailor racing a small dinghy on open water"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="events__content card">
      <div class="events__header">
        <h2 id="events-heading">Our Next Events</h2>
        <a
          class="link-chip"
          href="https://www.fremontsailingclub.org/2023-calendar-562573-358418.html"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
        >
          Go to calendar
        </a>
      </div>

      <article class="event-item">
        <p class="event-item__date">12 April 2026</p>
        <h3>2026 Sail-A-Dinghy Day</h3>
        <p>
          Join the Shoreline Lake event day and connect with the local small boat sailing community.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://shorelinelake.com/upcoming_events.html"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
        >
          Event details
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="event-item">
        <p class="event-item__date">3 May 2026</p>
        <h3>2026 Spring Series, Day 1</h3>
        <p>
          Preseason practice day is still TBD. Racing is at Shoreline Lake in Mountain View.
        </p>
        <div class="event-item__links">
          <a
            href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/yJPMdsg94msvBMUN7"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
          >
            Map
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://www.fremontsailingclub.org/results.html"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
          >
            Racing pages
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="club-note wrap">
    <p>
      Come join us to sail, whether you bring a boat of your own or crew with one of our members.
      Visit the membership page to join or renew, and check the current calendar for upcoming club events.
    </p>

    <div class="club-note__actions">
      <a
        class="button"
        href="https://www.fremontsailingclub.org/membership.html"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer"
      >
        Join or renew
      </a>
      <a
        class="button button--secondary"
        href="https://www.fremontsailingclub.org/commodores-comments.html"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer"
      >
        Commodore’s Comments
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="accent-band" aria-hidden="true"></section>
</main>
